What is After Action Review (AAR) Software for Training?
After Action Review (AAR) Software for Training consists of specialized digital platforms designed to facilitate structured debriefing processes following training exercises, simulations, or operational activities. These tools capture, analyze, and visualize performance data to help teams understand what happened, why it happened, and how to improve future outcomes. Core functionalities often include automated data logging from simulation systems, video playback synchronization, performance metrics tracking, collaborative annotation tools, and actionable insights generation.

